{"tid":1810134,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［都係捱唔住］「里人文化」月底停業　昨日起清倉散貨　業界感惋惜","createTime":"2020-01-03T15:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T05:18:03.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e9d4e1f7e1d4b9d13d4f222b1023214b9170be51","tid":1810134,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T15:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cAHj7Js.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAHj7Js.png&h=dfdcd703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n代理台港書籍為主的出版及發行商「里人文化」年前已傳出虧損嚴重，經營困難的消息。日前，里人文化在Facebook 公布本月將進行「歇業清倉」。《立場新聞》曾向里人文化查詢有關「歇業」一說，員工表示須向老闆了解，至今未有回覆。有業界人士形容里人文化結業為「書業寒風」，深表可惜。<br />\n<br />\n上月28日，位於荃灣的里人文化在Facebook 專頁發帖宣布，1 月 2 日至 1 月 31 日將進行「歇業清倉」，台版書三至四折，港版書六五折，更有大量精選特價書僅售五元。《立場》曾向里人文化查詢有關「歇業」一說，員工表示須向老闆了解，至今未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n業界紛感可惜  憂本地書業未來<br />\n<br />\n歇業消息傳出後，本地出版社「次文化堂」社長彭志銘亦在 Facebook 發帖形容事件為「書業寒風」，並附上里人文化於12月29日發出的停業公告。公告提到「里人已無力向前」，「那疲憊的手、發酸的腿，再不能挺起走下去」，定於本月 31 日正式「關燈停業」，又感嘆「無奈無言」。<br />\n<br />\n彭志銘寫道：「資深的發行公司，再捱不下去，宣告結業」，又指里人文化是難得有心的發行商，其結業對於中小出版社而言為「一大災難」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sQziDQg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsQziDQg.png&h=a7835ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外，與里人文化長期合作發行的本地出版社 dirty press 總監張小鳴接受《立場》訪問時表示，早在一兩年前已經感受到里人的經營壓力，亦預感始終都會有這一天的到來。他形容自己心情複雜，「惋惜遺憾」。他指出，近年整個書業發展面臨巨變，讀者與書店減少，反映發行商壓力越來越大，營業額不足，「里人或其他同業淡出或歇業，是預期之中」。但他相信或許危機可帶來轉機，也是時候反思怎樣重新建立一個適合中小型出版社的營銷網路。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/里人文化-月底停業-昨日起清倉散貨-業界感惋惜/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96-%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD-%E6%98%A8%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7%E6%B8%85%E5%80%89%E6%95%A3%E8%B2%A8-%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E6%84%9F%E6%83%8B%E6%83%9C%2F&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDnljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=9927c9e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96-%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD-%E6%98%A8%E6%97%A5%E8%B5%B7%E6%B8%85%E5%80%89%E6%95%A3%E8%B2%A8-%E6%A5%AD%E7%95%8C%E6%84%9F%E6%83%8B%E6%83%9C%2F&h=68551013\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/里人文化-月底停業-昨日起清倉散貨-業界感惋惜/</a>"},{"pid":"4db2d99d0ab1b09219890fa51d8a46a94742e678","tid":1810134,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c87091b68315b5e619daffdcedfc877b524fbd7","tid":1810134,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:00:52.000Z","msg":"個模式都轉左，更加多人去睇網上連載小說，貪佢夠方面"},{"pid":"7fae2659c660d4f5895052821596377ec06c9622","tid":1810134,"uid":116967,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:32:08.000Z","msg":"我鍾意睇紙本書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38f0b3ab2d466a0021162281669d78c4071100e","tid":1810134,"uid":100337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7fae2659c660d4f5895052821596377ec06c9622","tid":1810134,"uid":116967,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:32:08.000Z","msg":"我鍾意睇紙本書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:48:07.000Z","msg":"我都係，用手機睇可能冇乜